metadataAttributes.title: IAC-21.5 - Prohibit Non-Privileged Users from Executing Privileged Functions
metadataAttributes.summary: Mechanisms exist to prevent non-privileged users from executing privileged functions to include disabling, circumventing or altering implemented security safeguards / countermeasures.
